# LOG — {{project_name}}

Append-only journal of every meaningful action taken, **newest at the bottom**.
This is the durable memory of the investigation across sessions. Use
[TEMPLATE.md](TEMPLATE.md) for each entry.

**What earns an entry:** {{#if use_gates}}a gate changing state, {{/if}}an
artifact arriving, a hands-on result (a run, a capture, a test), a dead end that
rules something out, a correction to a prior understanding. **Not** every
conversation turn or intermediate thought — those stay in the working session
until they settle into one of the above. When in doubt, batch: one entry per real
checkpoint, written when the picture is clear.

Record error strings, identifiers, and versions **verbatim** — they're how you
search threads/docs later and how mis-identification gets caught.

